Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:09.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can barely sleep these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and I can't concentrate at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:15.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When was that you become unable to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:19.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's because of a women with a strong awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:23.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dr. Mizushima
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:25.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:27.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:29.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please look.\N{\3c&H585657&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:32.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Fukuhara asked Dr.Hino
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:35.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to show him the role-playing of\Ninteractive psychotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:38.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, from the middle it has just become\Na love counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:40.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:46.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Although I think I shouldn't wait\Neven 1 day and confess to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the courage doesn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:53.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Confession ... You don't think you have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:56.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No\NIt's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:01:00.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She is usually humming AKB48 songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I could express to you\N“I love you”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you don't answer\NEven if you look bothered
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:18.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When I heard the lyrics
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:20.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understood the supremacy of confession
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:23.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I love and not convey my feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:26.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll come to be a pessimistic and useless man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:28.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:31.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But...\N{\3c&H585657&}But?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:36.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, even if you confess\Nit doesn't necessarily mean that you'll get a good answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:39.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's it, if I get rejected..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,your current relationship\Nwill become awkward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:44.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And there is more risk that your state of mind\Nwill fall more and more into insecurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:48.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's that what you feel?\N{\3c&H585657&}That's why, I'm in a trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:51.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:53.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let exhale slowly our breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:57.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:02:00.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara-kun, listen,\NAs I said in the lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:05.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,love is something transitory.\NIt is a state, such as a mental illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:10.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will you fell with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi..Hino-rin it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:22.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I meet you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:24.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:30.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why?..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:32.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:34.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what's wrong?\NIt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:36.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So in other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:39.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the conclusion is that it is very dangerous\Nto lose the reason for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:41.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about the hormone balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When in love, the male hormone in men
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and in women, the female hormone,\Neach will increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:50.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For men, it increases the aggressive behavior,\Nand while they will be able to work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:54.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the gentleness is reduced.\NIf we talk about our work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We'd no longer hear\Nthe story of patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To attend the patient with empathy,\Nbecomes really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:02.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Those are the possible\Nconsequences that may occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:04.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fukuhara kun,\NWhat kind of doctor do you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that is..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:13.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to be one that can draw close to the mind\Nof each person as Dr. Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:16.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to be a psychiatrist that\Ncould be able to help any patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, you should refrain from love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:23.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Regarding a psychiatrist,falling in love\Nis more hassle than what it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:26.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My favorite comedian also has this saying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,comedian?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:32.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Falling in love it's the first step for the transformation"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:42.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's have a cup of tea.\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:49.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is why Dr. Hino is still single until now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:53.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Though, he is great as a psychiatrist\NAs a man ....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He is problematic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh ..that also is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:04.64,Self tought,,0,0,0,,So, now let's move forward with no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.14,Self tought,,0,0,0,,I'm you our ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:12.20,Self tought,,0,0,0,,This is a story of a doctor that saves
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.75,Self tought,,0,0,0,,the lost sheep of this modern era.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:24.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:29.15,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late introduction,\NI'm a psychiatrist, Hino Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:39.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:59.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The major best-selling author, the novelist\NMr. Kazama Shinnosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even the fact to be considered,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it is an honor to be designated as\Nhis attending physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:06.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,His latest work, received bad reviews,\Nhe has fallen into a slump
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,His mood is fairly blocking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, contact Hino-kun.\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why Hino?\NI can solve this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because it's really important that the psychiatrist\Nhas affinity with the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your contender is much better on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have Dr. Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:27.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,After hospital today, come without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have a patient that I want you\Nto be in charged of, Hino-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:38.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well then, come to the Kinosa at 7 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that the Ryōtei (traditional restaurant)\Nfrom the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's it, Is there something\Nwrong about the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:50.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You've became quite a photographer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:53.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You want to broadcast it on the Internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:57.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, until the time comes.\NLet's wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,These are the most excellent psychiatric doctors\Nin the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:05.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm the Head of the department of Psychiatry,\NProf. Miyagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:08.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My name is Hino,\NI look forward working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You guys probably have read some of\NMr Kazama novels, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:15.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Certainly, whatever you write, has become\None best-seller after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Also my wife,\Nstarted reading it with pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could I get your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's a total failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:28.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Not at all, my wife found it\Nextremely interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Critics gave a harsh time to Mr. Kazama.\NLet's leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:34.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's because they don't know \Nthe suffering of creating something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:37.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NNow, let's have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kazama, director Naito,\NWelcome, Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good evening, I'm Yumeno.\NI'm Koyume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, let's have some sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:54.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because tonight, it's Director Ennoji's treat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, let's have some party!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, no.\NIt's on director Naito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:07:00.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha! Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin, we meet again
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:06.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin?\N{\3c&H585657&}Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, have one.\N{\3c&H585657&}I don't want sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:17.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:20.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kazama, it's a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:22.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She's Hosaka-kun, your secretary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:25.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That person is an impostor! You are not Mutsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:28.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kazama\NWhat are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's just like that, it's a different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:34.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who instigated this?\NWho brought such a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. ..\N{\3c&H585657&}I see
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are using my name without permission
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:41.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and wrote this boring book!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is why I was criticized so badly\Nby the critics
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:49.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who called you? Ey Was it Naito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kazama, Hosaka-kun and I, neither of us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,would do such a thing..\N{\3c&H585657&}This is your conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:57.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm being wiped out from the literary world\Nbecause of you both!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Kazama, let's calm down.\N{\3c&H585657&}Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:02.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of this as your doctor.\N{\3c&H585657&}Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:08.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is bad, call an ambulance.\N{\3c&H585657&}Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:11.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr., Are you ok?\N{\3c&H585657&}Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:18.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr.\N{\3c&H585657&}Mr. Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, Stop it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Get off me! What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director's special case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hold firmly his body.\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We'll go with 1 ampoule of Diazepam by IV
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You put poison in that syringe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When he becomes quiet\Nadministrate haloperidol
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:39.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And take a head CT and MRI\N{\3c&H585657&}Stop that injections!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:41.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's good I got injured\N{\3c&H585657&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:47.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin will take care\Nof this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:50.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's ask a surgery dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mizushima, Mizushima
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:57.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?\N{\3c&H585657&}Sorry, it's just that..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's a person who injured a finger ..\N{\3c&H585657&}Ok, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Later, later\N{\3c&H585657&}Later?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're close to Dr. Hino, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. well, we live close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:13.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where does Dr. Hino live?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:17.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\3c&H585657&}And, do you know when is his birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:21.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to know so much\Nabout Dr. Hino?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:24.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be?\NAre you Dr. Hino's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:29.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, why do you have\Nsuch a scary face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hasumi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About Mr. Kazama..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't know until I see his scans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh-!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:57.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,With this..we will be connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:17.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:26.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but\Nyou'll have to wait a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:31.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kazama Shinnosuke\Nis a metaphor genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:34.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In other words, a prodigy at metaphors
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:39.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That transcendent literary style,\Nsurpasses by far the imagination of ordinary people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm a big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, he is said to be a treasure \Nof Japan literary world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You also know that?, Rintaro\N{\3c&H585657&}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Around the main character,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,odd characters constantly\Nappear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:58.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and it's particularly distinctive,\Nthis flying squirrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A flying Squirrel! \N {\3c&H585657&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But the work he published recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,has received bad critics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, it's weird that those things affected
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:12.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,so much at such a great writer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,People are fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:18.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,People who are believed to be strong\Nare more fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:24.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Now, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:27.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:36.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I made it using a recipe \Nfrom my favorite comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Fried curry and bean sprouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:48.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Bean sprouts and fried ... \Neh? Isn't it a salad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:51.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since the 70% of a salad it's air
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to eat it, is similiar to eat air.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that also a conclusion \Nfrom your favorite comedian?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot the mashed potatoes.\NYup?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:03.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder from who.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:13.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:17.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Let's meet on your day off\NYumeno
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:03.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The patient fell in a sudden excitement state
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,when that happened, he hit on the head,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and that caused a mild brain contusion into \Nthe right temporal lobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:10.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For the excited condition,\Nhaloperidol was used to calm him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:13.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,With the exception of the brain contusion,\Nno other organic abnormalities were found.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:17.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For now, there are none\Nsurgically points to be addressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:20.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because of the circumstances and his behaviour before the falling down,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:24.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and judging from the diagnosis\Nof the images of the SPECT scan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's seems this is paranoid schizophrenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:30.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The first thing is to prescribe risperidone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:33.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It would be an established tactic to expect the symptoms to improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:37.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see..\Nas expected it's paranoid schizophrenia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:40.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it too early to judge so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Hino-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, not from the image of the SPECT,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:47.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,also it was obserbed a blood flow decrease\Nin the parietal lobe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,which is frequently to find in schizophrenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:53.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Miyagawa have you talked to the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have been in direct contact with the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You understand that I said it many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:01.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The misdiagnosis is born from being misled\N by the patient's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:04.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, what can you conclude about him mistaken a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:09.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Kazama, it's a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's Hosaka-kun, your secretary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That person is an impostor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:15.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is the Capgras syndrome.\N{\3c&H585657&}Capgras syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:18.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can you describe it so as to we can understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Capgras delusion syndrome,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:23.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,also called "the illusion of look-alikes",\N is a disorder in which a person holds a delusion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:27.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and they're convinced that a familiar person\Nhas been replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,by an identical-looking impostor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:33.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, paranoid schizophrenia it's a safe bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:35.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But..can't we just
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,get one interview anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:40.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are the basis for Hino-kun to say that even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:43.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., say it heavily please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:47.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The basis..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just.. for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:52.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think we want to listen carefully to the patient's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? You want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You can't restrain Paranoid schizophrenia\Njust with psychotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:14:59.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In other words, Hino-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,what you're saying about this patient, is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:03.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Hasumi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:06.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is like a fight of judo and karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:10.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The clothes may resemble\Nbut the way of fighting is completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:12.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well.\NSuch a place would do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:16.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:19.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,About the attending physician ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's ask Dr. Miyagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.25,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:35.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. "just for some reason"\Nwas weak
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:44.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Get out! You're not Mutsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's your favorite flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Get out! you! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I do not want to see something like your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Get out! - Get out! \N{\3c&H585657&}Mr..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:55.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kazama-san. \N{\3c&H585657&} Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:57.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?\N{\3c&H585657&}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:02.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't need a doctor! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The fact is that..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:09.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,my friend is Kazama-san's fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:12.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you could,\Nwould you give me your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:15.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No way!\N{\3c&H585657&}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:19.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because of my friend's recommendation\NI was allowed to also read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:25.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What was quite interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't understand anything of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:30.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate doctors!\N{\3c&H585657&}Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you get it, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:37.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kazama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:40.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,May I ask you one question as a reader?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:47.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The protagonist of this novel is in love with the flying squirrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:51.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr., Is the flying squirrel near you, even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:58.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:01.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It can not be seen anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:06.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It had already disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:13.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When did it disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Think about it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:22.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That figure while flying..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:31.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino ...what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, this is an examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:39.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kazama is my patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Leave\N{\3c&H585657&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm relly sorry Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We have your medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:52.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:18:14.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:41.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:52.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I became Mr. Kazama's secretary 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:55.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:19:02.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, so, his first novel since you started as his secretary,\Nwas this 'Illusion'?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:05.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's it.\N{\3c&H585657&}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:10.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And his writing, where did he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:13.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He confined himself at a Karuizawa hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:16.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:22.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But ... at that time did something change\Nin his behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:25.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:27.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kazama has an amazing ability to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:30.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He was able to write it in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:32.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:37.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, from "Illusion" onwards,\Nin Mr. Kazama's novels,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:41.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,a strange and rather interesting character
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:47.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,since that moment, Mr. Kazama created a new style\Nthat earned him high appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:50.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're really well informed.\N{\3c&H585657&}Well, actually..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:53.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've just read it last night.\N{\3c&H585657&}Ah..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:56.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My first intention was to study this\Nas to read his thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:59.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But then this cute flying squirrel\Nappeared...yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and finally I became absorbed in reading\N{\3c&H585657&}I see
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:05.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here, please\N{\3c&H585657&}Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:09.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Like, when it (the squirrel) makes him feel rejuvenated,\Nwhen it clings to his back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:13.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,or when it makes terrible mischiefs and interferes with his work
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:16.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I like that part, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It hates the peanuts in the Kaki-peanuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:21.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A squirrel that eats Kaki-peanuts without peanuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,does it even exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Does it? I wouldn't know..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:34.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,From about when does Mr. have this sort of behaviour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since about three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:40.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demons outside! Good fortune come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:43.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. stop it please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:46.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You! Are you a demon?\NEh? or a god of wealth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:49.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which one? Answer!\N{\3c&H585657&}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't hear about such deadline for the manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. I have told you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:54.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was also present at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You two are conspiring against me\Nto make me lose my manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:01.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demons! After all, you are demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:05.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Demons outside"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:07.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:11.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, as soon as possible come with\NProf. Miyagawa to the directors' office.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll go later,\NSo, three months ago..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:17.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is urgent!\N{\3c&H585657&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:22.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-kun has been interfering with the treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:28.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If Mr. Kazama's delusions\Naren't due to Capgras syndrome,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:31.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it may not be good administering medicine\Nthat will suppress the delusion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:33.75,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could you stop meddling with my patient's treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:35.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Before deciding the name of the disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:37.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,wouldn't it be better to hear the patient's story?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd be a time loss\N{\3c&H585657&}Loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:43.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't the time facing the patients, the most important one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Whenever the treatment is up to Hino-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you can spend talking\Ndozens of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:51.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The publisher director is begging us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:55.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,books are not been sold in this era,\Nonly his books will sell when put out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:57.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,They want him to write as soon as possible his new work,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:22:00.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,or the company will collapse.\N{\3c&H585657&}I'll issue an inmediate result.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:04.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.\NPlease, leave Mr. Kazama to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:09.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-kun\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:11.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In the future I forbid any contact with the patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:15.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,also do not meet with the patient's staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:17.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:20.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's with that {\i1}"Ok"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:22.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miyagawa, you're messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:25.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because a psychiatrist like you was present\Nthe patient got annoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:29.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't rely only on medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:33.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's all?\NYou're saving something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:36.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Also, Ennoji, it's Ennoji.\N{\3c&H585657&}That's it, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:40.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's with {\i1}"In the future I forbid any contact"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:43.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around!\Nacting so refined, when your belly is showing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:47.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're thinking something evil\NYour brains are black!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:49.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, certainly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:53.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that person is black-hearted haha
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:56.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,feeling refreshed?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:23:00.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here, take some sugar and\Nthe fatigue in your head will come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:03.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, only one.\N {\3c&H585657&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:05.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:10.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:14.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Life..what's it about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:16.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:21.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well Yeah, life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:24.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is full of regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:26.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is too sweet\NI'll make some tea
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:28.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:33.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:35.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.62,0:23:43.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To send such a mail to the busy Hino-rin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:46.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was an annoyance, right?\NFrom Yumeno..?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.71,0:23:50.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a patient.\NHeh, it seems..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:54.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Let's meet on your day off.\NYumeno
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:23:57.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The spring has finally come for you.\N{\3c&H585657&}It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:24:01.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,hahaha\Nhahaha..you have spilled some.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:05.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was not a annoyance,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.66,0:24:09.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:12.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,All day long, I've been thinking..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.11,0:24:16.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?!\N{\3c&H585657&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.14,0:24:19.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,..of you.\N{\3c&H585657&}Hey stop, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:21.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, send it.\N{\3c&H585657&}It has been sent!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:23.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.14,0:24:39.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here, here, she answered!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.63,0:24:42.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? {\i1}I'm Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.11,0:24:45.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, tomorrow at one p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.61,0:24:50.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,come to meet me at the geisha house, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:53.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Geisha house? Hey you, a geisha house..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.21,0:24:57.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,a geisha?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.13,0:25:06.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm just going because it's rude\Nto neglect a promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.12,0:25:08.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is not a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.12,0:25:11.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because to be good psychiatrist,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.12,0:25:14.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I should refrain from falling in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.16,0:25:18.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, then Yasuke-san
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.20,0:25:20.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.62,0:25:25.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.62,0:25:27.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.64,0:25:32.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.63,0:25:35.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, welcome.\N{\3c&H585657&}Thank you for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.63,0:25:38.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The other day, the doctor also wasn't cornered, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.15,0:25:40.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.62,0:25:46.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today you're going out with Yumeno, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.14,0:25:48.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but what do you mean by\N'going out'?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.63,0:25:50.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.63,0:25:54.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A day like today, is to play with a geisha\Noutside the parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.12,0:25:56.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.19,0:26:01.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is the fee. (for a geisha's companionship)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.62,0:26:05.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.13,0:26:08.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.63,0:26:10.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.52,0:26:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(454.4,53.8)}As the fee, 100 000 yen\N will be charge to Hino Rintaro-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.12,0:26:16.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see you brought a lot of sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.66,0:26:18.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,whenever you want, please
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.63,0:26:27.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,3 months ago..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.63,0:26:30.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes?\NNothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.12,0:26:35.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just now, you were problably thinking\Nof your patients, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.64,0:26:37.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.61,0:26:41.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kazama?\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.18,0:26:44.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kazama was always drunk when coming to the parlor,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.60,0:26:47.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and it was the frist time he was troubled by 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.60,0:26:50.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that lady who is his secretary,\Nthat never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.61,0:26:53.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is that so..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.13,0:26:54.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.63,0:27:00.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In the middle of our date\Nplease forget about the patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.15,0:27:02.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just put your attention on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.72,0:27:06.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.12,0:27:10.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, I have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.11,0:27:14.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The other day, when you passed through the cherry trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.13,0:27:18.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,why didn't you notice me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.63,0:27:22.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Althought I think you heard my voice\Nyou just followed ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.69,0:27:24.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was wondering, why was that..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.72,0:27:28.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, that was my twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.11,0:27:30.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.45,0:27:34.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm often mistaken with\Nmy sister, since we look much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.62,0:27:38.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So you have a twin..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.12,0:27:40.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh ~.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.11,0:27:52.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.18,0:27:54.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Right!, go go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.62,0:27:57.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,will you keep us forever waiting?\NAkira-san
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.62,0:28:01.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you can't prepare it after two days,\Nby the beginning of next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.13,0:28:03.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the parlor,\NIs that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.11,0:28:08.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You'll not be in Shinbashi\Nanymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.15,0:28:11.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then please, come to pick me up, please\NI'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.62,0:28:16.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, that's enough!\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes, that came up fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.63,0:28:19.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? Does she have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.13,0:28:22.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.63,0:28:24.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san, here
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.62,0:28:28.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.71,0:28:35.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry\NI.. lied to you just before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.11,0:28:38.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was a lie that I have a twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.11,0:28:40.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That was a lie..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.62,0:28:44.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice Hino-rin because,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.12,0:28:48.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was really upset that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.21,0:28:58.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're finally here\N{\3c&H585657&}After all, 10 million is impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.13,0:29:01.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.64,0:29:03.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's FX?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.12,0:29:08.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're not Akira-san,\Naren't you Yumeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.66,0:29:11.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.21,0:29:14.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could you pay within few days just 1/3?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.64,0:29:19.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,with your important relatives,\Nthat would be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.12,0:29:25.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.63,0:29:36.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In fact, that night,\Nthere was a phone call from the hospital my father is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.14,0:29:39.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your father,\Nis his health delicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.14,0:29:45.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.13,0:29:49.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san, please tell me if there's \Nsomething I can do to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.62,0:29:55.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My father has a lung cancer,\Nand it has merged with bronchitis,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.12,0:29:58.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've been told that surgery is not possible anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.13,0:30:01.51,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At last, I was able to find a doctor that will take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.51,0:30:03.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But according to that doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.13,0:30:06.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the latest treatment\Nwill cost 3 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.65,0:30:10.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,3 million ...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.72,0:30:12.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.62,0:30:16.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In the middle of a fun date,\NI end up with such a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.63,0:30:26.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.12,0:30:32.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san, it's gonna be OK.\NPlease, don't cry anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.11,0:30:34.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I will help with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.12,0:30:45.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.62,0:30:50.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please make a deposit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.71,0:30:55.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Aizawa Akira"\N{\3c&H585657&}It's my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.13,0:30:58.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, but
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.60,0:31:02.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come at least once to my examining room?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.62,0:31:04.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,examining room?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.13,0:31:07.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry if I surprised you\Nwith such a phrase
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.13,0:31:10.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, please\Nit'll help you to have brighter feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.17,0:31:13.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At lunch break,\Nwe'll have a cup of tea together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.62,0:31:18.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Let's eat this over there\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.63,0:31:25.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.12,0:31:29.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.12,0:31:51.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.61,0:32:19.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.10,0:32:24.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aizawa-sama, here.\NPlease confirm the amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.12,0:32:27.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here is the cash\NPlease confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.13,0:32:31.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.62,0:32:43.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What yah doing, hurry, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.61,0:32:59.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.61,0:33:02.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We'll meet next week, right? Akira..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.61,0:33:05.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,-san.. that's not,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.13,0:33:07.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.12,0:33:24.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.64,0:33:27.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah hello\Nwith the director Ennoji, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.64,0:33:29.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's Yumeno
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.11,0:33:40.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ennoji, yes\NHello,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.17,0:33:44.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.14,0:33:47.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The special patient, Kazama-san\Nhas been complaining of strong abdominal pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.61,0:33:49.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What about Dr. Miyagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.11,0:33:51.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since the Prof. is busy with meetings\Nsince the beginning of the week,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.63,0:33:53.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,can you see him instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.62,0:34:00.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This foreign body was found \Nin the x-ray of his stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.69,0:34:02.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you think?\N{\3c&H585657&}Flying squirrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.61,0:34:05.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.13,0:34:09.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You've been reading too much of Mr. Kazama's novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.61,0:34:12.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Look carefully, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.62,0:34:17.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.14,0:34:21.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,with this, you'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.73,0:34:24.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.11,0:34:27.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.63,0:34:30.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He should have swallowed it by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.12,0:34:34.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's penetrating the stomach wall,\Nit may not come off without an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.12,0:34:39.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demons outside! Good fortune come!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.63,0:34:42.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Please, stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.18,0:34:45.12,Self tought,,0,0,0,,"Taking only seeds of kaki from the kaki-peanuts
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.12,0:34:47.13,Self tought,,0,0,0,,while eating them deliciously..."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.13,0:34:49.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A squirrel that eats Kaki-peanuts without peanuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.62,0:34:52.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}does it even exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.12,0:34:55.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does it? I wouldn't know..
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.61,0:35:00.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Its flying figure
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.61,0:35:03.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.13,0:35:05.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.12,0:35:08.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did you bring such a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.14,0:35:11.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.68,0:35:14.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, Rintaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.12,0:35:26.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There is no need for you to prove\Nwhether you are or not
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.62,0:35:29.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the real Mutsumi
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.13,0:35:35.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The answer should be provided\Nby Mr. Kazama himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.11,0:35:47.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.13,0:35:53.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is a symbol of Kazama-san's anguish.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.60,0:35:57.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.62,0:35:59.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.64,0:36:03.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kazama-san,\Nnow, Mutsumi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.71,0:36:06.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she is about to enter this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.11,0:36:08.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.63,0:36:10.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.62,0:36:14.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.20,0:36:25.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This way
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.11,0:36:40.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well then, eat them in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.12,0:37:29.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.11,0:37:31.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's enough already
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.13,0:37:34.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.13,0:37:37.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.13,0:37:45.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't be so irresponsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.62,0:37:50.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, one more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.63,0:37:52.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,eat them
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.66,0:37:59.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.61,0:38:04.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't you eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.13,0:38:05.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.63,0:38:08.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr., are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.62,0:38:20.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In reality, you are aware that she is the real Mutsumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.21,0:38:22.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,aren't you Mr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.12,0:38:38.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mutsumi has peanuts allergy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.12,0:38:40.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And you were aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.14,0:38:44.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why you desperately try\Nto stop her from eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.19,0:38:49.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The fact that she is Mutsumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.13,0:38:52.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you have that awareness somewhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.63,0:38:58.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kazama-san, your delusions and hallucinations,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.12,0:39:02.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think they aren't due \Nto paranoid schizophrenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.21,0:39:11.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The flying squirrel for you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.64,0:39:15.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is someone irreplaceable?\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.62,0:39:20.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The illusion that if you reach for it, disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.63,0:39:24.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But the flying squirrel that comes out\Nin your novel..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.61,0:39:27.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that has spent 15 years by your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.68,0:39:31.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,weren't you suppose to continue supporting\Nyour literary creation?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.64,0:39:35.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shut up, quack doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.13,0:39:38.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You love Mutsumi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.63,0:39:40.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.62,0:39:46.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr., you've been sitting there\Nfrom this morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.67,0:39:49.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please rest a little{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.14,0:39:53.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't it cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.13,0:39:57.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, maybe it's a bit cold\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.15,0:40:09.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.14,0:40:11.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.13,0:40:14.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.13,0:40:16.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mutsumi\N{\3c&H585657&}Yes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.15,0:40:20.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.19,0:40:22.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.74,0:40:25.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is from me, to thank you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.14,0:40:27.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.65,0:40:30.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.63,0:40:33.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah It's beautiful! Mr.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.62,0:40:36.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look at it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.17,0:40:38.22,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}got it, got it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.22,0:40:39.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's really beautif{\i1}ul Mr.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.63,0:40:47.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can't make\NMutsumi happy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.13,0:40:52.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why is that?\N{\3c&H585657&}Isn't it obvious..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.14,0:40:55.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,60..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.14,0:40:58.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Once comfortably in something\Nlike a warm happy family,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.68,0:41:01.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I couldn't continue to write novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.63,0:41:05.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Marry that man
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.13,0:41:07.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demons outside!\NMr.! Mr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.13,0:41:09.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please,\Nstop throwing peanuts
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.15,0:41:10.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to Mutsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.65,0:41:15.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are plenty replacements for you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.13,0:41:21.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do not come here anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.13,0:41:25.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.13,0:41:35.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You released your flying squirrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.13,0:41:37.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though, that illusion was the source of your inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.65,0:41:40.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So when you lost it, you became insecure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.65,0:41:42.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.12,0:41:46.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps those feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.14,0:41:50.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,were showing Mutsumi\Nto you as another person or a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.73,0:41:52.73,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.15,0:41:57.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The ring became for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.15,0:42:01.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,another form of the flying squirrel,\Nwasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.64,0:42:09.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you want to remove it with a surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.62,0:42:15.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.64,0:42:17.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's fine in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.11,0:42:25.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kazama-san
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.13,0:42:28.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My favorite comedian has a saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.13,0:42:33.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Life is an illusion, we're a bunch of illusions"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.12,0:42:39.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.14,0:42:42.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kazama-san is a genius of illusions
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.15,0:42:46.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and that is your uniqueness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.63,0:42:49.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, what about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.14,0:42:53.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Short-term psychotic disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.69,0:42:56.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is my diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.65,0:43:01.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do I need any treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.63,0:43:04.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.13,0:43:07.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In your case, Kazama-san\Nit's something temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.64,0:43:12.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think there's no need for help,\Nif you don't need help in social life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.11,0:43:19.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,so self-important..
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.12,0:43:25.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You'll have many fans waiting for your next novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.64,0:43:27.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,so noisy,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.62,0:43:32.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,quack doctor, I know that,\Nyou don't need to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.15,0:43:36.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since this is the end,\Ndon't interfere with my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.64,0:43:45.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your friend...\Nwhat's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.63,0:43:47.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.63,0:43:51.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your friend who is my fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.61,0:43:56.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yuriko\NIt's Yuri as in Lily (he's explaining the kanji)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.63,0:44:10.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!\NIt'll maker her really happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.14,0:44:21.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.14,0:44:23.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.63,0:44:28.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mutsumi
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.64,0:44:32.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm fine on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.12,0:44:37.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In the future, I won't\Nhire another secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.66,0:44:44.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.14,0:44:48.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks for taking care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.62,0:44:53.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.13,0:44:58.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The happiness for a woman, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.13,0:45:01.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The happiness of a woman..
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.17,0:45:04.74,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I envy her.\N{\3c&H585657&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.74,0:45:22.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.62,0:45:40.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kazama-san won't need a treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.63,0:45:45.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, it isn't paranoid schizophrenia?\N{\3c&H585657&}Right, it's a short-term psychotic disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.63,0:45:48.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Its symptoms have ceased.\N{\3c&H585657&}They have ceased?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.62,0:45:52.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, Kazama-san is a genius of illusion,\Nhe has a great personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.65,0:45:57.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There is no need for medication,\Nit'll be fine if he's discharged soon from hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.11,0:46:00.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director, this is a simplistic and biased\Ndiagnosis from Hino
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.13,0:46:02.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I do not accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.11,0:46:04.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, which one is correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.63,0:46:06.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\N{\3c&H585657&}You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.62,0:46:09.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But..\N{\3c&H585657&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.14,0:46:11.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When there is no need of treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.14,0:46:13.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There will be no need of hospital charges\Nand the fee for the differential bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.69,0:46:16.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The doctor's fee can't be removed.\N{\3c&H585657&}That would be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.13,0:46:18.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.61,0:46:21.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.64,0:46:28.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-kun\Nis excellent as an attraction panda, but
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.61,0:46:32.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If all the symptoms of the patients\Nare caused due to their personalities
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.69,0:46:35.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,then as a psychiatric you won't\Nhave even one patient left.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.12,0:46:40.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,maybe it's impossible for him to become a Prof...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.62,0:46:43.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director, there's something I want to show you.\N{\3c&H585657&}yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.14,0:46:48.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a call from director Naito.\N{\3c&H585657&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.11,0:46:50.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's Ennoji
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.13,0:46:55.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kazama has started writing a new novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.20,0:46:57.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.12,0:47:01.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's great,\Nour psychiatry dep. is excellent after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.62,0:47:05.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We'll show our gratitude the next time..
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.13,0:47:07.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We are looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.63,0:47:11.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hasumi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.67,0:47:17.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.64,0:47:20.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Take hold of your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.14,0:47:27.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"In my belly dwells a small ring"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.63,0:47:32.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"One day, I swallowed and tried to digested it"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.67,0:47:36.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"but, my body rejected it."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.12,0:47:40.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"In that garden\Nyou could see it right through"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.15,0:47:44.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"between the singing of the frogs at the tree frog"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.13,0:47:46.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"it's an eviable thing"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.13,0:47:50.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"when you swallowed something that can't be digested"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.64,0:47:56.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"It washes everytime you drink water from the mouth to the stomach."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.13,0:48:01.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I would also like to wash the beaten parts of my brain,"
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.62,0:48:04.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"in that way, at least just once."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.62,0:48:10.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Cheers for good work, Dr. Rintaro\N{\3c&H585657&}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.64,0:48:13.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Although it's the time to say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.20,0:48:15.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,why is there a red line drawn on the book I lent you!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.63,0:48:17.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry Mizushima
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.63,0:48:21.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh, I've received a bonus from Dir. Ennoji, 
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.64,0:48:24.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, everyone, without refraining,\Nplease eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.12,0:48:26.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry,\Ntwo servings of kalbi (Korean-food), please
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.64,0:48:29.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A beer please.\NI also want a beer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.13,0:48:32.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The bonus, it's a lot of money?\NLet's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.70,0:48:34.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah\Nmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.62,0:48:36.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, yesterday morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.64,0:48:39.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you were sending\Na lot of money somewhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.62,0:48:42.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At the Hospital ATM,\Nnot at one transaction
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.12,0:48:46.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But 30 times.\N30 times, so you mean 3 million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.14,0:48:49.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where did you remit such big amount?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.15,0:48:54.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be? Dr. Hino\Nonly could send it to support that woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.12,0:48:56.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.61,0:49:01.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,did you do it? to that geisha,\NYumeno-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.63,0:49:03.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.63,0:49:07.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she was quite suspicious,\Ntrying to know your address.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.15,0:49:09.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As expected, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.72,0:49:14.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.12,0:49:16.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To paid for his father's treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.84,0:49:18.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're caught by a classic move.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.63,0:49:22.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,classic? Is it so?\N{\3c&H585657&}It's an awfully classic one
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.61,0:49:26.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, and I thought I was paying high tuition fees.\NYou better give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.62,0:49:29.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, and there was also the price for going outside..
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.15,0:49:32.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,going... outside, a price?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.72,0:49:35.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That was also high.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.13,0:49:39.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.11,0:49:42.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You were eating yakiniku (roasted meat)?\N{\3c&H585657&}I ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.65,0:49:45.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,C'mon, I don't want my Taiyaki (fish-shaped pancak),\Nwith your yakiniku smell
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.71,0:49:54.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.63,0:49:57.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah welcome back
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.12,0:50:00.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because of your help\Nmy father's treatment was a success
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.12,0:50:02.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.92,0:50:06.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, what are you doing here\Nthis late?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.61,0:50:08.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I.. here ..
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.64,0:50:11.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I thought of trying to return this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.12,0:50:23.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The medical fees were covered by \Nthe kindness of some relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.14,0:50:26.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.83,0:50:29.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.61,0:50:31.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really, Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.64,0:50:36.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah ... cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.69,0:50:38.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's its name?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.61,0:50:40.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's Yasuke
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.63,0:50:43.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yasuke  Yasuke
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.11,0:50:48.13,Self tought,,0,0,0,,If you want to be a good psychiatrist\Nyou should avoid things like love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.13,0:50:51.64,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Love is transient,\Nsimilar to a mental disorder
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.64,0:50:55.17,Self tought,,0,0,0,,By no means, do not ever\Nfall in such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.17,0:50:57.67,Self tought,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
